    <title>Crispy rosemary and garlic potato galettes with smoked salmon</title>
    <updated>2025-05-17T17:33:31.043226+00:00</updated>
    <content type="html">&lt;h1 style="text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;"&gt;Crispy rosemary and garlic potato galettes with smoked salmon&lt;/h1&gt;
