    <content type="html">&lt;h1 style="text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;"&gt;Spiced honey cake&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;br&gt;
        &lt;img src="https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/spiced-honey-cake.webp" style="text-align:center;"/&gt;
        &lt;br&gt;
        &lt;p style="font-family:sans-serif;&gt;I usually pick a floral or citrusy honey for this cake, like wildflower or clover rather than a dark, strongly flavored variety, but you can use any honey you prefer. Don’t skip the sliced almonds on top—they add a lovely crunch and texture.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
